<p>After much waffling and flip-flopping, I re-joined the wiki in November of 2016. I first came back into chat in early December, and people have been tolerant of me since. This is where I start actually liking some of my writing.</p>
<h2 id="toc55"><span><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dontcallitacomebackbecauseidontknowifillstay">Closure</a></span></h2>
<p>My lowest-rated page. I hope it stays that way.</p>
<p>This is kind of a vent piece, related to someone I had mixed feelings on at the time. I shan't say who. But this was my grand return to the wiki. Not much else to say.</p>
<h3 id="toc56"><span><a href="/scp-2487">SCP-2487</a>- Postman Chasers</span></h3>
<p>My first earnest attempt to get back into writing. Alexylva finally starts punishing mail fraud. I honestly still find this piece to be pretty funny and charming, even a few years after the fact. Even if it is just an over-the-top version of &quot;Dogs Chase Postmen&quot;.</p>
<h3 id="toc57"><span><a href="/happy-howlidays">Happy Howlidays</a></span></h3>
<p>Forget the Hague, I'm pretty sure that <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(778357); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(778357); return false;">ProcyonLotor</a></span> wants me <em>dead</em> for this pun. I like this a fair bit better than 12 Days.</p>
<h3 id="toc58"><span><a href="/an-unconventional-tail">An Unconventional Tail</a></span></h3>
