<h1 id="toc59"><span>2017: Renaissance</span></h1>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Take&nbsp;me&nbsp;home,&nbsp;country&nbsp;roads</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
