<p>Like my work in any capacity? Want to make sure I can be a starving artist that eats once in a while? Why not buy me a coffee through <a href="http://ko-fi.com/ihpkmn?">http://ko-fi.com/ihpkmn?</a> Any amount helps.</p>
<h2 id="toc87"><span>Living Will</span></h2>
<p>In case I decide to do something utterly stupid and start deleting articles en masse, or go inactive for a period of six or more months, I hereby give the following people retroactive collaboration privileges on my articles.</p>
<p>All S &amp; C Plastics Works and works related to Nexii: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=388108&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="Djoric" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=388108)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;">Djoric</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;">Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gg-crono" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(295496); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=295496&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="GG Crono" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=295496)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gg-crono" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(295496); return false;">GG Crono</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7061118); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7061118&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7061118)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info