<p>All works related to the Church of the Broken God: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2938475&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="Zhange" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2938475)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhange" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2938475); return false;">Zhange</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="HammerMaiden" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;">HammerMaiden</a></span>, and any other user that wishes to take up the mantle of Bumario, Trunion or Hedwig.</p>
<p>All other works are under the purview of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(778357); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609288480" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(778357); return false;">ProcyonLotor</a></span> and any individual they trust enough.</p>
<p>Everything I've done can be found if you dig far enough back in my Sandbox history. Everything that can't can probably be found on the Wayback machine.</p>

